{"tid":1372963,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"娘親頭先睇Live話⋯⋯","createTime":"2019-07-27T14:12:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T14:15:15.000Z","uid":276382,"like":6,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ffacf9564137d420704130b0af870fbd08baa6a1","tid":1372963,"uid":276382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:12:30.000Z","msg":"前線勇士舉木板舉得好辛苦<br />\n而且舉著木板就失去左一隻手嘅攻擊能力<br />\n於是佢諗左條絕世屎橋<br />\n用<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">廁所板</span></span></strong>黎做護甲<br />\n用廁所板套落條頸上面<br />\n個蓋向下擋住個身<br />\n既可以保護膊頭<br />\n又唔使全程舉住木板<br />\n比狗咬嘅時候轉動廁所板就擋到受襲部位<br />\n而且可以做近戰武器<br />\n有狗埋身一野拍落去<br />\n廁所板咁硬<br />\n就算有頭盔都會比聲波震到<br />\n就係唔知應該用木廁板好定係瓷廁板好"},{"pid":"dde5737aa40757955512897d50e72e7c261e7b07","tid":1372963,"uid":169195,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:13:44.000Z","msg":"俾人一拉你成個人就扯低"},{"pid":"842583c5bf8127504231234ad1a2384f4117484b","tid":1372963,"uid":232370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:14:23.000Z","msg":"咪on9啦"},{"pid":"09bcc0357cf1727c945c1fdf5617d70b9968e248","tid":1372963,"uid":24534,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:14:25.000Z","msg":"頸背好痛"},{"pid":"378e29c1bc9504ab5d88269f30236bdc92da59f1","tid":1372963,"uid":116289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df02222e131d57988a2df3046bc69e5e75856eb8","tid":1372963,"uid":263618,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:15:02.000Z","msg":"俾人拉果陣頸都斷埋<br />\n死都還好<br />\n唔死的話變頸以下地方完全唔郁動<br />\n<br />\n利申： 專業醫學意見"},{"pid":"f0bfad900aac7a4a81dc44aaf9badc0d5e84a05e","tid":1372963,"uid":44916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:15:15.000Z","msg":"用個入屎忽嘅放上頭，好柒"}]}